00:17:09,112 --> 00:17:09,612




281
00:17:09,612 --> 00:17:11,489
Vamos, Yawara, dame una buena pose.

282
00:17:11,489 --> 00:17:13,783
Deja de poner esa cara rara.

283
00:17:13,992 --> 00:17:16,119
¡Perdón por tener una cara rara!

284
00:17:17,495 --> 00:17:20,665
¿Por qué esa actitud? Es una engreída.

285
00:17:20,665 --> 00:17:21,124



286
00:17:21,124 --> 00:17:25,628
