Eres un estúpido.
Desperdiciaste una gran primicia.

363
00:22:30,517 --> 00:22:32,602

364
00:22:32,727 --> 00:22:34,979
Ya conseguiremos otra.

365
00:22:35,522 --> 00:22:36,773
Pero...

366
00:22:36,773 --> 00:22:37,273


367
00:23:24,070 --> 00:23:26,072
